ech tend to make them sell quickly. If you’ve been waiting for an affordable, decently powerful Windows laptop below the $500 mark, you might want to snag this one quickly.\n\nSee our roundup of the best laptops for other suggestions.\n\nThis HP laptop with solid specs is a fantastic deal for $325"}
